    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="546">
  <marc:subfield code="a">French, with some religious pieces in Latin (f. 1r-6r, 68v-72v, 76v-88v), some songs in Italian (f. 34v-36r, 58r-59r, 61v-63r, 64v-65r), and one song in English (f. 89v-92v).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
